---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import myPhoto from "/public/photo.webp";
const personalImageAlt = "Mikel Echeverria, Backend & Full Stack Engineer";
---

<article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_200px] gap-12 items-start">
  <div class="text-pretty order-2 md:order-1">
    <div
      class="space-y-6 text-[var(--ink)] opacity-90 leading-relaxed text-lg sm:text-xl [&>p>strong]:font-semibold [&>p>strong]:text-[var(--primary)]"
    >
      <p data-i18n-html="about.content">
        Soy <strong>Mikel Echeverria</strong>, un <strong>Backend & Full Stack Engineer</strong>. Mi
        enfoque combina rigor técnico con comunicación efectiva para construir sistemas escalables
        end-to-end. Además, exploro continuamente la <strong>Inteligencia Artificial</strong> y los <strong
          >modelos generativos</strong
        > para desarrollar soluciones robustas que optimicen procesos y aporten valor real.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center md:justify-end">
    <Image
      width="200"
      height="200"
      src={myPhoto}
      alt={personalImageAlt}
      class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-xl shadow-[var(--primary-muted)] ring-1 ring-[var(--border)] transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.03]"
    />
  </div>
</article>
